--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-13)
B: Fix bug introduced with Jinja2 style improvements

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
I: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'

* Version 0.2.6 (2018-12-11)
I: Minor Jinja2 syntax improvements
I: Move 'haproxy_exporter-current.link' task from 'install' to 'enable'

* Version 0.2.5 (2018-08-29)
B: Remove configuration files from install sequence (execute notify handler)

* Version 0.2.4 (2018-08-28)
I: Ensure user's home directory is being removed during remove sequence

* Version 0.2.3 (2018-08-28)
B: Fix remove sequence (stop service before removing group and user)
I: Correct task names

* Version 0.2.2 (2018-08-28)
I: Reorganize and improve folder structure

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-08-24)
I: Escape 'haproxy.scrape-uri' value

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-08-24)
F: Add support for 'haproxy_exporter_haproxy_scrape_uri' option (haproxy.scrape-uri)

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-08-23)
I: Remove directories 'haproxy_exporter_data.dir' and 'textfile_collector.dir'
I: Ensure file 'node_exporter.sysconfig' is being create during installation
I: Flush handlers after installation tasks for file 'haproxy_exporter.service'
I: Only reload systemd when file 'haproxy_exporter.service' changes
I: Change login shell to '/sbin/nologin' for service user
I: Minor YAML syntax improvements

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-08-23)
F: Initial release
